## ğŸŒ± Project Overview

**GreenSteps Community Gardens** is an interactive, multi-page educational website designed to empower South African communities through sustainable food production, environmental education, and local development programs.

This project demonstrates advanced front-end development skills through HTML5, CSS3, and JavaScript â€” focusing on usability, interactivity, and accessibility. The site includes SEO optimization, a fully validated contact form, and dynamic features such as a lightbox image gallery, FAQ accordion, and search filtering.

