1. **Clone this repository:**
   ```bash
   git clone https://github.com/SpheCodes/WEDE5020-POE.git
   cd WEDE5020-POE
   ```

2. **Open in your browser:**
   Simply open `index.html` in any modern browser (Chrome, Edge, Firefox).

3. **Optional (Live Preview in VS Code):**
